sunami, which is scientifically more accurate.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>  <p style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#0c0c0c\"><span style=\"font-family:Garamond,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">Tsunamis can be triggered by a variety of disorders (disturbance) in the sea, such as earthquakes, shifting plates, or volcanic eruption under the sea. Tsunamis can occur when the seafloor moves suddenly and undergo a vertical displacement. </span></span></span></span></span></span></p>  <p style=\"text-align:right\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#0c0c0c\"><span style=\"font-family:Garamond,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:small\"><em>Taken from: englishclas.com</em></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>  <p><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#0c0c0c\"><span style=\"font-family:Garamond,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">The text mainly tells us about &hellip;</span></span></span></span></span></span></p> ', 'how the tsunami can get to the land', 'the cause of tsunami', 'the effects of tsunami', 'the origin of the name ‘tsunami’', 'the place where the tsunami happened', 'sedang', 'd', '2', '2019-09-16 07:26:00', '2019-09-16 07:26:00'),
