rines and pavilions set high on the slopes of sacred Mt. Agung.</span></p>  <ul>  <li>  <p style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-family:Garamond,serif\"><strong>Kuta</strong></span></p>  </li> </ul>  <p style=\"margin-left:29px; text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-family:Garamond,serif\">Kuta Bay, with its long stretch of white sand and brilliant sunset, has attracted swarms of visitors since its rediscovery by surfers and sun worshippers in the 1970s.</span></p>  <p style=\"margin-left:29px; text-align:left\">&nbsp;</p>  <p style=\"text-align:right\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#0c0c0c\"><span style=\"font-family:Garamond,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:small\"><em>Taken from: bestworldtourism.com</em></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>  <p style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"color:#0c0c0c\"><span style=\"font-family:Garamond,serif\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>  <p style=\"margin-left:29px; text-align:left\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#0c0c0c\"><span style=\"font-family:Garamond,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">Bali&rsquo;s largest nature reserve </span></span></span><span style=\"color:#0c0c0c\"><span style=\"font-family:Garamond,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:small\"><u>encompasses</u></span></span></span><span style=\"color:#0c0c0c\"><span style=\"font-family:Garamond,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:small\"> 70.000 hectares of . . . . (line 9).</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>  <p style=\"margin-left:29px; text-align:left\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#0c0c0c\"><span style=\"font-family:Garamond,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">The underlined word means . . . .</span></spa